Chemical composition. Relevant secondary metabolites are diterpenes like andrographic acid, their glucosides (deoxyandrographolide-19β-D-glucoside) and dimers (bis-andrographolides A, B, C, and D) and labdane diterpenoids like andrographolide, neoandrographolide; flavonoids (methoxylated flavones, flavanones, chalcones); steroids (β-sitosterol (
 Koteswara Rao et al., 2004; 
 Akbar, 2011; 
 Dai et al., 2019; 
 Hanh et al., 2020). Andrographolides are considered the active metabolites and chemical markers of this species.
